<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 20:07:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着以色列军队的施压行动，加沙拉法的苦难加剧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/misery-deepens-in-gazas-rafah-as-israeli-troops-press-operation/articleshow/110092108.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110092108.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在过境点关闭的情况下，援助人员努力向拉法流离失所的巴勒斯坦人分发物资。以色列军方加强针对与埃及边境隧道的行动。赫茨尔山公墓举行纪念仪式，纪念阵亡士兵。联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构报告称，行动开始前共有 130 万巴勒斯坦人在拉法避难，其中有 36 万巴勒斯坦人上周已经离开拉法，其中许多人在 7 个月期间已经逃离了其他地区的冲突。以色列和哈马斯之间的一个月战争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 16:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/misery-deepens-in-gazas-rafah-as-israeli-troops-press-operation/articleshow/110092108.cms</guid></item><item><title>家人称尼日利亚枪手在绑架数十人后寻求谈判</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerian-gunmen-seek-talks-after-abducting-dozens-families-say/articleshow/110092399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110092399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据武装人员联系的 5 名受害者家属称，武装分子上周在尼日利亚西北部绑架了 105 人，要求与扎姆法拉州政府进行谈判，而不是支付赎金。袭击者劫持了扎姆法拉比尔宁-马加吉地方政府辖区村庄的居民。家人接到绑架者的电话，敦促政府进行谈判。扎姆法拉的信息专员批评了主张与绑架者谈判的个人，称政府拒绝了拟议的和平协议倡议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 16:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerian-gunmen-seek-talks-after-abducting-dozens-families-say/articleshow/110092399.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈萨克斯坦谋杀案引发家庭暴力改革</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-murder-case-in-kazakhstan-led-to-domestic-violence-reforms/articleshow/110090548.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110090548.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈萨克斯坦最高法院判定前经济部长宽迪克·比什姆巴耶夫（Kuandyk Bishimbayev）犯有酷刑和谋杀妻子罪，判处他 24 年监禁。此案引发全国愤怒，促使人们呼吁对家庭暴力采取更严厉的惩罚。比辛巴耶夫最初否认有罪，但后来承认殴打妻子萨尔塔纳特·努科诺娃，导致她死亡。他的亲戚巴赫特詹·拜扎诺夫（Bakhytzhan Baizhanov）因帮助掩盖谋杀案而被判处四年徒刑。在公众的广泛抗议和伸张正义的请愿之后，该案件促使哈萨克斯坦加强了虐待配偶的法律。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:30:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-murder-case-in-kazakhstan-led-to-domestic-violence-reforms/articleshow/110090548.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普：中国移民在美国组建“军队”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-chinese-migrants-forming-an-army-in-us/articleshow/110090167.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110090167.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-chinese-migrants-forming-an-army-in-us/articleshow/110090167.cms</guid></item><item><title>苏纳克称英国处于“十字路口”但拒绝举行大选</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/sunak-says-uk-at-crossroads-but-refuses-to-call-election/articleshow/110089903.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110089903.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相苏纳克周一坚称，陷入困境的执政党保守党可以赢得大选，尽管民意调查始终显示相反的结果，但拒绝设定投票日期。这位英国领导人表示，他“有信心”工党将连续第五个任期获胜，但也承认自 2010 年以来退出政府的工党最终可能会失败。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 13:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/sunak-says-uk-at-crossroads-but-refuses-to-call-election/articleshow/110089903.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本将制定2040年脱碳战略和产业政策</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-to-craft-2040-strategy-of-decarbonization-and-industrial-policy/articleshow/110088685.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110088685.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本政府决定在 2024 年 3 月底前制定脱碳战略和面向 2040 年的产业政策。​2040 年战略预计将完善去年的计划，为长期投资提供更多可预测性，同时增强国内企业的竞争力日本产业省产业科学技术环境政策局局长畠山洋二郎表示。告诉记者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:49:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-to-craft-2040-strategy-of-decarbonization-and-industrial-policy/articleshow/110088685.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫辞去巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟主席职务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-prime-minister-shehbaz-sharif-resigns-as-president-of-pml-n/articleshow/110087301.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110087301.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦总理谢巴兹·谢里夫辞去巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟纳瓦兹（PML-N）主席职务。他已向穆斯林联盟-谢里夫（PML-N）领导人纳瓦兹·谢里夫（Nawaz Sharif）正式递交辞呈。鉴于这一事态发展，PML-N 定于 5 月 28 日在拉合尔举行总理事会会议，选举新总统。最初，该党打算在5月11日召开这次会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-prime-minister-shehbaz-sharif-resigns-as-president-of-pml-n/articleshow/110087301.cms</guid></item><item><title>报道新冠病毒的中国公民记者在预计出狱当天状况不明</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/status-of-chinese-citizen-journalist-who-reported-on-covid-unknown-on-day-of-expected-prison-release/articleshow/110085832.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110085832.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;张展因报道武汉新型冠状病毒肺炎 (Covid-19) 疫情爆发的初期阶段而被判四年徒刑，但她失踪了，预计她将于周一获释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/status-of-chinese-citizen-journalist-who-reported-on-covid-unknown-on-day-of-expected-prison-release/articleshow/110085832.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩真主党声称袭击造成以色列士兵受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-claims-strikes-that-wounded-israeli-soldiers/articleshow/110084163.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110084163.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;黎巴嫩伊朗支持的真主党组织周一声称对这次袭击负责，以色列称这次袭击造成该国北部的四名士兵受伤，这是七个多月冲突中最新的跨境火灾。该组织在一份声明中表示，周一早上，真主党武装分子向边境另一边的以色列梅卡瓦坦克发射了“一枚制导导弹”，“在密切监视敌人的动向后”将其摧毁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-claims-strikes-that-wounded-israeli-soldiers/articleshow/110084163.cms</guid></item><item><title>“美国扣留了以色列有关哈马斯领导人的‘敏感情报’”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-withholding-sensitive-intelligence-on-hamas-leaders-from-israel/articleshow/110083900.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110083900.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府建议与以色列分享有关哈马斯领导人所在位置的重要信息。这种共享取决于以色列是否在拉法发动大规模军事行动。该信息来自《华盛顿邮报》的报道。美国希望通过提供有价值的信息来阻止大规模入侵。这些信息可以帮助以色列找到哈马斯领导人并寻找秘密隧道。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-withholding-sensitive-intelligence-on-hamas-leaders-from-israel/articleshow/110083900.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯前总统梅德韦杰夫用“特殊弹药”威胁北约</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/former-russian-president-medvedev-threatens-nato-with-special-ammunition/articleshow/110083527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110083527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:32:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/former-russian-president-medvedev-threatens-nato-with-special-ammunition/articleshow/110083527.cms</guid></item><item><title>“随着普京准备核力量，德国可能征召青少年入伍”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-may-draft-teens-in-army-as-putin-readies-nuclear-forces/articleshow/110083256.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110083256.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:22:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-may-draft-teens-in-army-as-putin-readies-nuclear-forces/articleshow/110083256.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着一些美国大学毕业典礼出现挑衅行为，校园内的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动逐渐减少</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pro-palestinian-protests-dwindle-on-campuses-as-some-us-college-graduations-marked-by-defiant-acts/articleshow/110082578.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110082578.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:06:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pro-palestinian-protests-dwindle-on-campuses-as-some-us-college-graduations-marked-by-defiant-acts/articleshow/110082578.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总统经济顾问因批评将印度领土纳入尼泊尔100卢比纸币地图而辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-presidents-economic-advisor-resigns-after-criticising-inclusion-of-indian-territories-in-map-on-nepal-rs-100-notes/articleshow/110081496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110081496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-presidents-economic-advisor-resigns-after-criticising-inclusion-of-indian-territories-in-map-on-nepal-rs-100-notes/articleshow/110081496.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他的军队在俄罗斯袭击中陷入“激烈”的边境战斗</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskyy-says-his-army-is-locked-in-fierce-border-battles-amid-a-russian-assault/articleshow/110078783.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110078783.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskyy-says-his-army-is-locked-in-fierce-border-battles-amid-a-russian-assault/articleshow/110078783.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国法院支持情报机构将极右翼政党列为涉嫌极端主义案件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-court-backs-intelligence-agencys-designation-of-far-right-party-as-suspected-extremist-case/articleshow/110078044.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110078044.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/german-court-backs-intelligence-agencys-designation-of-far-right-party-as-suspected-extremist-case/articleshow/110078044.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚伊布火山再次喷发，洪水中喷出巨大的火山灰塔</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-mount-ibu-erupts-again-spews-huge-ash-tower-amid-floods/articleshow/110070289.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110070289.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度尼西亚东部的一座火山周一喷发，在当局上周将警报级别提高到第二高后，一座巨大的火山灰塔喷向天空超过五公里（三英里）。目前还没有造成任何损失或人员伤亡的报道，但图像显示，北马鲁古省哈马黑拉岛的火山灰柱冲上天空。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesias-mount-ibu-erupts-again-spews-huge-ash-tower-amid-floods/articleshow/110070289.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯边境城市一公寓楼遭炮击后部分倒塌，多人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/apartment-building-partially-collapses-in-a-russian-border-city-after-shelling-several-killed/articleshow/110068221.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110068221.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员称，俄罗斯边境城市别尔哥罗德一栋公寓楼周日部分倒塌，造成至少 13 人死亡、20 人受伤。他们将这座建筑的毁坏归咎于乌克兰的炮击。网上视频显示救援人员在建筑物楼梯间的残骸中寻找幸存者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 03:25:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/apartment-building-partially-collapses-in-a-russian-border-city-after-shelling-several-killed/articleshow/110068221.cms</guid></item><item><title>“为什么年轻的俄罗斯女性想嫁给中国男人”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-young-russian-women-want-to-marry-chinese-men/articleshow/110067676.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110067676.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近的网络趋势已经浮出水面，其中一些短视频通过展示外国对中国的钦佩来激发民族主义情绪，尤其是来自名叫娜塔莎和索菲亚的俄罗斯年轻女性的钦佩。这些视频描绘了他们说着流利的普通话，赞扬中国文化，同时批评俄罗斯男人“醉酒和懒惰”。她们赞扬中国的社会和技术进步，并表示希望在与中国男性的婚姻中承担传统的家庭角色，例如做饭和抚养孩子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 03:14:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-young-russian-women-want-to-marry-chinese-men/articleshow/110067676.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谴责拜登说“如果人质获释明天就停战”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-biden-for-saying-truce-tomorrow-if-hostages-freed/articleshow/110064123.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110064123.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯谴责美国总统乔·拜登关于加沙可能停火的声明，称这是谈判的挫折。拜登提到，如果哈马斯释放在袭击中扣押的人质，“明天”可能会实现停火。由于以色列的军事行动，由埃及、卡塔尔和美国斡旋的谈判陷入僵局。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 22:58:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-biden-for-saying-truce-tomorrow-if-hostages-freed/articleshow/110064123.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>